gradle tasks --all 常见命令

# Application tasks
-----------------
=> bootRun - Run the project with support for auto-detecting main class and reloading static resources
启动项目

# Build tasks
-----------
=> assemble - Assembles the outputs of this project.


=> bootRepackage - Repackage existing JAR and WAR archives so that they can be executed from the command line using 'java -jar'

=> build - Assembles and tests this project.
构建项目

=> buildDependents - Assembles and tests this project and all projects that depend on it.

=> buildNeeded - Assembles and tests this project and all projects it depends on.

=> classes - Assembles main classes.

=> clean - Deletes the build directory.
删除构建目录

=> testClasses - Assembles test classes.

=> jar - Assembles a jar archive containing the main classes.

# Build Setup tasks
-----------------
=> init - Initializes a new Gradle build.
初始化构建

=> wrapper - Generates Gradle wrapper files.
生成包装器

# Documentation tasks
-------------------
=> javadoc - Generates Javadoc API documentation for the main source code.

# Help tasks
----------
=> buildEnvironment - Displays all buildscript dependencies declared in root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

=> components - Displays the components produced by root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'. [incubating]

=> dependencies - Displays all dependencies declared in root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

=> dependencyInsight - Displays the insight into a specific dependency in root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

=> dependencyManagement - Displays the dependency management declared in root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

=> dependentComponents - Displays the dependent components of components in root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'. [incubating]

=> help - Displays a help message.

=> model - Displays the configuration model of root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'. [incubating]

=> projects - Displays the sub-projects of root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

=> properties - Displays the properties of root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

=> tasks - Displays the tasks runnable from root project 'Building_a_RESTful_Web_Service'.

# IDE tasks
---------
=> cleanEclipse - Cleans all Eclipse files.
删除eclipse相关文件

=> cleanIdea - Cleans IDEA project files (IML, IPR)
删除IDEA相关文件

=> eclipse - Generates all Eclipse files.
生成eclipse相关文件

=> idea - Generates IDEA project files (IML, IPR, IWS)
市场IDEA相关文件

# Verification tasks
------------------
=> check - Runs all checks.

=> test - Runs the unit tests.

# Other tasks
-----------
=> cleanEclipseClasspath

=> cleanEclipseJdt

=> cleanEclipseProject

=> cleanIdeaModule

=> cleanIdeaProject

=> cleanIdeaWorkspace

=> compileJava - Compiles main Java source.

=> compileTestJava - Compiles test Java source.

=> eclipseClasspath - Generates the Eclipse classpath file.

=> eclipseJdt - Generates the Eclipse JDT settings file.

=> eclipseProject - Generates the Eclipse project file.

=> findMainClass

=> ideaModule - Generates IDEA module files (IML)

=> ideaProject - Generates IDEA project file (IPR)

=> ideaWorkspace - Generates an IDEA workspace file (IWS)

=> processResources - Processes main resources.

=> processTestResources - Processes test resources.

